        <h1>A simple BF interpreter</h1>
        <p>This is a
            simple, non-optimizing interpreter for the esoteric language Brain****.
            All of the logic was done in about 50SLOC. There is no limit on memory
            (except the memory available on your machine), although negative memory
            addresses are not allowed.</p>
